{
  "stem": "868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, Don Giovanni got the blanks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sat in his room typing up the story, imagined fabricated stories, names, places of birth, date of birth, of every Jew that he had under his surveillance, under his protection.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then he gave the cards back, which were now blanks, blanks filled out, but who needed that special stamp, that embossed stamp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He gave it back to the underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The cards came back a little while later, stamped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He now faked the signature of the-- of the commissioner of police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he handed us, in Florence, those cards, like he handed them over to all the women hidden in Treviso.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, this card becomes of special importance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Slowly, the allied armies inched their way up the Italian peninsula.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They where still very far away from Florence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you may have heard of Monte Cassino, which is a major, major blocking of the Allied troops.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a monastery, sitting on top of a hill, commanding the view of the entire valley, blocking any advance of the Allied armies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And although the monastery itself had been the subject of constant heavy bombardments, the Germans still were deeply entrenched until the day they broke through.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And now, the Allied armies slowly inched their ways up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As they approached Florence, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans became more and more vicious.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Not just because they had to retreat, but there were also partisan sniper attacks on-- on them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one day, the whole orphanage-- which was a huge complex, it had classrooms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think there were about 250 children there at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It had classrooms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It had workshops for tailoring, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shoes repairs, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] woodworking, metalworking.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
